description:
Doree and Kate get a voicemail from a listener who’s reframing the narrative about her body after childbirth, discuss that weird urge many of us have to compare ourselves to our partner’s exes, and hear from a listener dealing with “house shame.”

To leave a voicemail for a future episode, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com. To learn more, visit forver35podcast.com.
